comments.body:
It seems that you wanted the following.
```
- INSERT INTO TIMESTAMP_TBL VALUES timestamp(('now'));
+ INSERT INTO TIMESTAMP_TBL VALUES timestamp('now');
```

Or,
```
INSERT INTO TIMESTAMP_TBL VALUES (timestamp('now'));
```

